Heart Rate Sensor

Summary
An application that detects your heart rate and show the datas on PC screen.
The sensor will be put on one of your fingers and sense the pulse signal from the finger tip.

Component Parts
Pulse sensor, Arduino board, PC, USB cable

Include what types of inputs/outputs/data it will use. You can also upload an image with a diagram showing how all those pieces are connected.

